prompts.frontCover: A charming and slightly wobbly, hand-drawn cartoon watercolor illustration of an elderly tortoise wearing a tiny, festive party hat, looking absolutely bewildered as a single, brightly colored birthday balloon tied to its shell slowly lifts its back legs off the ground. The tortoise has a comically surprised expression with wide eyes. Below the tortoise, in a beautiful, flowing, and readable handwritten cursive script, is the text "happy slightly older birthday". The entire scene is rendered in a soft, lighthearted watercolor style with visible paper texture, artistic brush strokes, and gentle color bleeds, creating a funny and endearing image. Flat 2D artwork.
